=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5477dc53116c3ec173ff7349eeeb86453373284","tid":1362687,"uid":170370,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"1. 類固醇，但要注意唔可以搽太密，否則會冇效同有反效果。早晚搽一次，搽到皮膚平滑可停。就算未好，如果用左一星期就要停一星期。如果之前長期勁搽，要停兩星期。<br />\n2. 用cetaphil/physiogel沖涼同保濕cream&amp;lotion。cream就早晚（沖涼後），lotion日頭用（嚴重者可一個鐘一次）。<br />\n3. 忍手唔好抓。<br />\n4. 止痕丸cetrizine（但呢個我食咗覺得冇咩分別）。<br />\n5. 衣著以棉質平滑鬆身為佳。<br />\n6. 避免出汗（盡量啦我都知好難），如有出汗就輕輕印乾再搽保濕lotion。<br />\n以上全部係皮膚科醫生教我，我兩年前都發得好勁，而家雖然未算好晒但都控制到好多了。我真係好多謝佢，希望都幫到大家。"},{"pid":"122a242503dd9b71c6ca9fe034b3afd502a0bb7e","tid":1362687,"uid":111181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0199fef2616143de4c8c999e556d0480ba791bd","tid":1362687,"uid":150653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"719ed079596786a8ec9346fa3d140bcbb377d5bd","tid":1362687,"uid":111181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d73e9b10bdda4d69195d986d5a9e74b6fe986ef","tid":1362687,"uid":150653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"係邊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"中醫叫人搽類固醇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4282122ec19388049482274eb69fc9f4085db03","tid":1362687,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"我個人就會沖完涼會先搽一浸蘆薈gel<br />\n等佢索曬之後再搽Nivea嘅保濕cream<br />\n情況改善咗好多<br />\n同埋每星期都要剪同剉甲<br />\n盡量出少嘅汗<br />\n出街可以嘅話盡量唔好孭背囊<br />\n因為會搞到背脊出曬汗容易出疹<br />\n戒口就冇咩特別去戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4b089ef3f1c05aa1f8c84d53279082aee23fef","tid":1362687,"uid":182042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,